out at the door unto them, and shut the door after him,"},{"id":"recz8BGnVVGLCnuKD","ref":"Gen.19.7","text":"And said, I pray you, brethren, do not so wickedly."},{"id":"recunmcQR70tG8yXP","ref":"Gen.19.8","text":"Behold now, I have two daughters which have not known man; let me, I pray you, bring them out unto you, and do ye to them as is good in your eyes: only unto these men do nothing; for therefore came they under the shadow of my roof."}]}
